00:27:46,244 --> 00:27:48,663
Warga di sekitar Joojin Chemical

430
00:27:48,746 --> 00:27:51,499
terus mengeluhkan sakit
selama bertahun-tahun.

431
00:27:51,875 --> 00:27:53,459
Dengan mewawancarai mereka,

432
00:27:53,543 --> 00:27:55,003
