- Pernyataan, Pak.

924
01:00:27,028 --> 01:00:29,405
- Pak, ada pernyataan?
- Pak!

925
01:00:29,489 --> 01:00:30,865
Tolong katakan sesuatu.

926
01:00:30,948 --> 01:00:32,950
- Pak!
- Di sini.

927
01:00:33,910 --> 01:00:35,703
Apa alasan interogasi ini?

928
01:00:39,707 --> 01:00:42,960
<i>Tusukan mematikan
yang menembus tumit Achilles.</i>

929
01:00:53,763 --> 01:00:55,556
<i>Situasi berubah,</i>

930
01:00:57,934 --> 01:01:01,562
<i>dinding yang semula kokoh mulai retak.</i>

931
01:01:32,927 --> 01:01:35,930
<i>Badai mendekat.
Kau harus bersiap menghadapinya.</i>

932
01:01:36,013 --> 01:01:38,516
<i>Aku sudah siapkan lantai dansa,
