936
01:01:47,024 --> 01:01:50,236
<i>Kurasa aku harus pastikan kau mengerti.</i>

937
01:01:50,319 --> 01:01:52,405
<i>Kupikir Menteri Song merencanakan sesuatu.</i>

938
01:01:53,030 --> 01:01:54,407
Nona Lee!

939
01:01:54,490 --> 01:01:56,951
<i>Tae-jun, kau seharusnya tahu</i>

